Maxima strode down the corridors, in search for Blackstorm.

Soon enough, she found the Predacon prodigy. 

Her crimson optics fell upon Blackstorm with Hevn as the door opened & she 
stepped into the room. Glaring at Hevn for a moment, then turning her attention 
to Blackstorm. 

"Hydras has a little... plan in mind. & you are a major part of it." That was 
all she said, since Hevn was present. 

Stepping aside, she then motioned to the doorway, for Blackstorm to obey 
orders & do as asked. 

--part1_6d.146e8d75.2c2f77e9_boundary
